<includeonly>
<infobox>
  <title source="title1">
    <default>{{PAGENAME}}</default>
  </title>
  <image source="image1">
    <default>[[File:{{#invoke:Reactors|get|{{PAGENAME}}|prop=image1|raw=1}}|frameless|60px]]</default>
    <caption source="caption-image1"/>
  </image>
  <group>
    <header>Reactor Information</header>
    <data source="cost">
      <label>Cost</label>
      <default>{{#invoke:Reactors|get|{{PAGENAME}}|section=Unit Information|key=Cost}}</default>
    </data>
    <data source="weight">
      <label>Weight</label>
      <default>{{#invoke:Reactors|get|{{PAGENAME}}|section=Unit Information|key=Weight}}</default>
    </data>
    <data source="required_tech_level">
      <label>Required Tech Level</label>
      <default>{{#invoke:Reactors|get|{{PAGENAME}}|section=Unit Information|key=Required Tech Level}}</default>
    </data>
    <data source="other_requirements">
      <label>Other Requirements</label>
      <default>{{#invoke:Reactors|get|{{PAGENAME}}|section=Unit Information|key=Other Requirements}}</default>
    </data>
    <data source="max_energy_level">
      <label>Max Energy Level</label>
      <default>{{#invoke:Reactors|get|{{PAGENAME}}|section=Properties|key=Max Energy Level}}</default>
    </data>
    <data source="recharge_rate">
      <label>Recharge Rate</label>
      <default>{{#invoke:Reactors|get|{{PAGENAME}}|section=Properties|key=Recharge Rate}}</default>
    </data>
    <data source="defensive_merit">
      <label>Defensive Merit</label>
      <default>{{#invoke:Reactors|get|{{PAGENAME}}|section=Properties|key=Defensive Merit}}</default>
    </data>
  </group>
</infobox>
</includeonly>
<noinclude>
== Reactor Template ==

This template renders an infobox for reactor pages. It automatically loads data from [[Module:Reactors_data]] based on the page name.

=== Automatic Data Loading ===

When used as <code><nowiki>{{Reactor}}</nowiki></code>, the template automatically queries [[Module:Reactors_data]] using <code><nowiki>{{PAGENAME}}</nowiki></code> as the lookup key. No parameters are required on reactor pages that exist in the data module.

=== Manual Override (Backward Compatible) ===

All parameters can be manually specified to override the automatic data:

<pre>
{{Reactor
  | title1 = Example
  | image1 = Example.jpg
  | caption-image1 = Example
  | cost = Example
  | weight = Example
  | required_tech_level = Example
  | other_requirements = Example
  | max_energy_level = Example
  | recharge_rate = Example
  | defensive_merit = Example
}}
</pre>

